data.description: A RARE CONDO WITH PRIVATE BALCONY. 2bed/2bath condo with white marble floor, black granite counters, white cabinets, light wood floor scheme rare in building. Located on the third floor, conveniently located near the pool area and parking. Parking space included. Overlooking front of the building - the “quiet side”. Close enough for easy access yet not loud. Concrete build ensures quietness. Recent updates include in-unit GE washer/dryer (2019), KitchenAid dishwasher (2020), Samsung wifi range/oven (2021), GE microwave (2021). HVAC repaired (2020) and cleaned thoroughly (2022), new bathroom sink (2022). Newly painted walls and carpets (2024). Amenities include 24 hour concierge, Olympic size swimming pool usable year-round, 3 tennis courts, state-of-the-art gym, meeting and club rooms, commercial area with shops. Pet friendly!
